line_1: In this lone cell I've dwelt;
line_2: To soothe the pangs I felt.

line_1: Nor war nor mis'ry in its precincts dwelt,
line_2: No mother by her bleeding offspring knelt.

line_2: Who no pangs of ambition or love had e'er felt:
